{"title":"青海诗歌","authors":["可国","歌行"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":4,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"青海诗歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社好比太阳红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原一步跨天庭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破帐篷变成了玉皇宫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马似彩霞羊如云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社好比太阳红。牛羊儿乘上了卫星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昆仑草原千里景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社的红旗飞腾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斩断了千年的穷根根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛羊儿乘上了卫星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红绿的光芒闪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一绺儿山来两绺儿山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山连川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洼洼里都栽上了电杆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几辈子帐房里黑黯黯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛圈里红绿的光芒闪。破木碗换成龙碗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几辈子披下的老羊皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送进了历史的博物馆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几百年用下的破木碗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧业社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换给了闪光的龙碗。幸福花映红牛羊圈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茯茶滚成牛血了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红葡萄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帐房里搭了架了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧业公社成立了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映红牛羊圈了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（可国、歌行）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}